## About 

These are materials for workshop held at the University of Tokyo on 12-15th November 2018. The main website for this workshop is found [here](https://sites.google.com/ut-biomet.org/statistical-methods-ws/) with thanks to [Hiromi Kanegae](mailto:kanegae@ut-biomet.org) from Graduate School of Agricultural and Life Sciences, University of Tokyo for setting it up.

## Lecturers

**Gota Morota** (GM) Virginia Polytechnic Institute and State University, USA<br>
**Diego Jarquin** (DJ) University of Nebraska-Lincoln, USA<br>
**Emi Tanaka** (ET) University of Sydney, Australia<br>
**Malachy Campbell** (MC) University of Nebraska-Lincoln, USA<br>
**Jessica Tressou** (JT) INRA, France<br>
**Hiroyoshi Iwata** (HI) University of Tokyo, Japan

